      "options": {
        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "\u003cfont color=\"#5794f2\"\u003e\n\u003cblockquote style=\"margin-top: 0px\"\u003e\n  \u003ch1\u003e\u003cb\u003eV. Rubin File Transfers\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/h1\u003e\n\u003c/font\u003e\n\n  \u003cli\u003eThis dashboard shows the top sources and destinations by volume and rate of all file transfers.\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eClick on an organization name in one of the tables to see the file transfer data dashboard for that organization.\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eThe slope graph below shows the top pairs of organizations by volume. Darker lines correspond with larger volume.\u003c/li\u003e\n \u003cli\u003eAll IPs have been de-identified.\n \u003cli\u003eAll times are displayed in browser local time.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/blockquote\u003e\n",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
